ZH: 我感到疲劳了，我需要休息一下。
EN: I'm feeling tired, I need to take a break.

ZH: 昨天晚上工作到很晚，现在我非常疲劳。
EN: I worked late last night, now I'm very tired.

ZH: 他疲劳地挥汗如雨地跑完了马拉松比赛。
EN: He ran the marathon exhaustedly, sweating profusely.

ZH: 在疲劳的状态下开车是非常危险的。
EN: Driving in a state of fatigue is very dangerous.

ZH: 长期缺乏睡眠会导致身体疲劳。
EN: Chronic lack of sleep can lead to physical fatigue.

ZH: 我的眼睛因为疲劳而感到不舒服。
EN: My eyes feel uncomfortable due to fatigue.

ZH: 考试之后，学生们都感到精疲力尽。
EN: After the exam, the students all felt exhausted.

ZH: 她在疲劳的情况下勉强完成了最后的报告。
EN: She barely managed to finish the final report in a state of fatigue.

ZH: 老板不允许员工在疲劳的状态下工作。
EN: The boss doesn't allow employees to work while fatigued.

ZH: 每个人都需要合理安排时间，避免疲劳。
EN: Everyone needs to schedule their time properly to avoid fatigue.

ZH: 长时间的运动让我感到身体疲劳。
EN: Prolonged exercise makes me feel physically exhausted.

ZH: 短时间内完成这么多工作真的让我疲劳不堪。
EN: Completing so much work in a short period of time really exhausts me.

ZH: 这个周末我打算休息一整天，摆脱疲劳。
EN: I plan to rest all day this weekend to shake off the fatigue.

ZH: 这份工作的压力让我感到疲劳不堪。
EN: The pressure of this job makes me feel utterly exhausted.

ZH: 早上跑步是预防疲劳的好方法。
EN: Running in the morning is a good way to prevent fatigue.

ZH: 这个周末我打算早点睡觉，来缓解疲劳。
EN: I plan to go to bed early this weekend to relieve fatigue.

ZH: 据说喝一杯咖啡可以消除疲劳。
EN: They say that drinking a cup of coffee can dispel fatigue.

ZH: 长途飞行后，我总是感到身体疲劳。
EN: I always feel physically fatigued after a long flight.

ZH: 训练比赛之后，队员们都感到筋疲力尽。
EN: After the training match, the players all felt completely exhausted.

ZH: 他看上去疲劳不堪，看来一整天都在工作。
EN: He looks utterly exhausted, it seems like he's been working all day.
